        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[Redis, RabbitMQ, 服务网关故障]]></title>
            <link>https://status.vmatrix.org.cn/incidents/3e958365</link>
            <guid>https://status.vmatrix.org.cn/incidents/3e958365</guid>
            <pubDate>Thu, 03 Dec 2020 23:46:32 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>我们接到系统报警，一台承载 Redis 与 RabbitMQ 的服务器宕机，服务网关受到部分影响。</p>
<div class="update-block">
          <div class="update-block-date">2020-12-04T01:45:00.000Z</div>
          <div class="update-block-content">
            <div class="update-block-title">Investigating</div>
            <div class="update-block-body">
<p>我们收到用户关于此次故障的反馈，并正在调查该问题。</p>
</div></div></div>
<div class="update-block">
          <div class="update-block-date">2020-12-04T02:02:00.000Z</div>
          <div class="update-block-content">
            <div class="update-block-title">Monitoring</div>
            <div class="update-block-body">
<p>我们重新启动了宕机的服务器，用户应已可以正常登录。我们仍在观察评测队列与服务网关的恢复情况。</p>
</div></div></div>
<div class="update-block">
          <div class="update-block-date">2020-12-04T02:46:00.000Z</div>
          <div class="update-block-content">
            <div class="update-block-title">Resolved</div>
            <div class="update-block-body">
<p>故障已解决。</p>
</div></div></div>
]]></content:encoded>
        </item>
